Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.54,0:19:25.68,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,284)\an9}小小房间 心心相连
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.68,0:19:31.26,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,284)\an9}将一切静静诉说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.26,0:19:37.44,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,284)\an9}当这个季节到来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.44,0:19:44.11,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,284)\an9}纵想寻你千百遍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.11,0:19:49.45,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,284)\an9}奈何你已不在世间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.45,0:19:55.00,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,284)\an9}我会永远铭记着你
